    "plan_content": "The plan is ready for your review. Here's a quick summary:\n\n**Single file to modify:** `src/event-emitter.ts`\n\n**Core design:**\n- One `Map<string, Listener[]>` as the backing store\n- **Snapshot strategy** for `emit` — copy the listener array before iterating so that mid-emit removals (self-removal, unsubscribe, one listener removing another) never crash or skip subsequent listeners\n- **Wrapper pattern** for `once` — a wrapper calls `off(event, wrapper)` then invokes the original listener\n- **Cleanup in `off`** — delete the map key when a listener array becomes empty, so `eventNames()` stays accurate\n\nAll 7 methods have detailed implementation steps in the plan file. The approach handles every edge case tested by the 29-test suite.",
